{
  "application": "Zeppelin",
  "other_software": [
    "Spark",
    "Hadoop"

    "spark_setup_type": "STANDALONE",
    "spark_local_dir": "/tmp/${USER}/spark",
    "zeppelin_local_dir": "/tmp/${USER}/zeppelin",
    "spark_job": "sparkpi",

    "spark_memory_fraction": "0.6",

    "spark_storage_memory_fraction": "0.6",
    "spark_shuffle_memory_fraction": "0.2",
    "spark_rdd_compress": "true",
    "spark_io_compression_codec": "lz4",

    "spark_job_classpath": "",

    "spark_job_memory": "2048",
    "spark_driver_memory": "2048",
    "spark_daemon_heap_max": "2000",
    "spark_environment_extra_path": "${HOME}/spark-my-environment",

    "spark_sparkwordcount_file": "file:///path/mywordcountfile",

    "magpie_local_dir": "/tmp/${USER}/magpie",

    "magpie_submission_type": "sbatchmpirun",
    "magpie_one_time_run": null,
    "magpie_pre_job_run": null,
    "magpie_post_job_run": null,
    "magpie_pre_execute_run": null,
    "magpie_post_execute_run": null,
    "magpie_environment_variable_script": "${HOME}/my-job-env",
    "magpie_environment_variable_script_shell": "/bin/bash",
    "magpie_remote_cmd": "ssh",
    "magpie_remote_cmd_opts": "",
    "mpirun_options": "-genvall -genv MV2_USE_APM 0",
    "magpie_startup_time": "30",
    "magpie_shutdown_time": "30",
    "spark_conf_files": "${HOME}/myconf",
    "zeppelin_conf_files": "${HOME}/myconf"
  }
}
